      </div>
      <div class="roadmap-body">
        <h3>Assess the Risk in Your Home</h3>
        <p>In Japan, every homeowner knows their building's age and retrofit history. In Turkey too, the starting point is this: when was your building constructed — before or after 1999?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="roadmap-step">
